&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The windows in the east elevation wall of the building shall be permanently glazed in obscured glass and
kept fixed shut.
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: In the interests of neighbouring amenity.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
